<chapter id="introduction">
 <title>Introduction</title>
  <para>&kfilereplace; is an application that performs search and replace of one or more strings in one or more files. The strings you want search for, may be literals or QT-like regular expressions. There are even other options that you may use to tune your search.
  </para>
</chapter>

