<sect1 id="kfilereplace-the-project-dialog">
 <title>The New Session Dialog</title>
 <para>The new session dialog is used to setup the basic parameters needed by KFileReplace to work. It consists of two page the "General" page and the "Advanced" page.
 </para>
 <sect2 id="kfilereplace-the-project-dialog-general-page">
