         </imageobject>
         <textobject>
           <phrase>Screenshot</phrase>
         </textobject>
       </mediaobject>
     </screenshot>
   </para>
   <para>
     When you want to begin a new session the first step is to click on the <link linkend="kfilereplace-the-toolbar">new session button</link>. Then you must enter the base path and a shell-like wildcards sequence to use as filter.
     <screenshot>
