         <imageobject>
           <imagedata fileref="path_options.png" format="PNG"/>
         </imageobject>
         <imageobject>
           <imagedata fileref="path_options.eps" format="EPS"/>
         </imageobject>
         <textobject>
           <phrase>Screenshot</phrase>
         </textobject>
       </mediaobject>
     </screenshot>
     Then you could set some usefull options, like searching in all the sub folders, doing a case sensitive search, enabling commands and/or regular expressions(please note that regular expressions and commands could slow down the speed performances!), doing a backup copy of each file that KFileReplace should modify.
     <screenshot>
       <screeninfo>Here's a screenshot of &kfilereplace;</screeninfo>
       <mediaobject>
         <imageobject>
           <imagedata fileref="general_options.png" format="PNG"/>
         </imageobject>
         <imageobject>
           <imagedata fileref="general_options.eps" format="EPS"/>
         </imageobject>
         <textobject>
           <phrase>Screenshot</phrase>
         </textobject>
       </mediaobject>
     </screenshot>
     Finally if you wish to start now then put a string in the search line edit widget and press "Search now" button, otherwise live the line edit widgets empty and press "Search later" button.
     <screenshot>
       <screeninfo>Here's a screenshot of &kfilereplace;</screeninfo>
       <mediaobject>
         <imageobject>
           <imagedata fileref="quick_options.png" format="PNG"/>
         </imageobject>
         <imageobject>
           <imagedata fileref="quick_options.eps" format="EPS"/>
         </imageobject>
         <textobject>
           <phrase>Screenshot</phrase>
         </textobject>
       </mediaobject>
     </screenshot>
   </para>
 </sect2>

 <sect2 id="kfilereplace-the-project-dialog-advanced-page">
